This little applet is designed to be extremely simple and easy to use tray applet for freerdp


Machine folder

The machines folder needs to exist in the executing assembly's directory. This folder will contain each of your machine files that you remote into. 

File format for freerdp
group=<mymachinesgroup>
machine=<ip/hostname>
username=<username>@<domain/ifnecessary>
password=<password>
type=rdp

File format for ssh
group=<mymachinesgroup>
machine=<ip/hostname>
username=<username>
password=<password>
type=ssh

File format for vnc
group=<mymachinesgroup>
machine<ip/hostname>
type=vnc
